# Graphiti Temporal Memory

## Supersedes

When a new ADR/decision replaces an old one:

- Emit `Supersedes` edge from new episode to prior
- Prefer Graphiti bi-temporal invalidation over silent overwrite

## conflicts_with

- Run `graphiti_memory_client.py conflicts` before GMP Phase 0 lock
- Surface unresolved conflicts in Phase 6 evidence Section 11
- Human resolves or documents each conflict before cutover

## Search-before-write (T1/T2)

Before lesson/manifest writes, search same `group_id` for near-duplicates.
